  "title": "Quantity Surveyor | Training Provided | Diploma | Bukit Merah | 5 Days | Up To $4.2K - 4461",
  "description": "<p><strong>Quantity Surveyor</strong><br />Salary: 3,000 - 4.200<br />Working Hours: Mon to Fri, 9am - 6pm<br />Location: Bukit Merah Central</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Involvement in the overall quantity surveying, cost & contract management of projects</li><li>Feasibility studies & early cost advice.</li><li>Preparation of cost estimate & cost plan</li><li>Value management & cost management</li><li>Advice and management of the overall procurement process</li><li>Preparation of tender & contract documentation</li><li>Evaluation of tenders received, analysis & reporting</li><li>Measurement and taking-off of quantities and quantification of works done</li><li>Valuation of progress payment claim, variation and final account</li><li>Attendance to project & site meeting</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Recognised Degree/Diploma in Quantity Surveying/Building or equivalent qualifications</li><li>2 to 5 years of relevant working experience in a consultancy firm preferred</li><li>Proficient in QS application and software</li><li>Training Provided</li></ul><p><br /><br /><strong>Email: supreme.jacksontan@gmail.com</strong></p><p><strong>Tan Yong Zhi (Jackson) | Reg: R24124461</strong></p><p><strong>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte. Ltd | EA No: 14C7279</strong></p>",
